reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater comfortable, soft, and stylish, with one mentioning it can be dressed down or up. They love the color, particularly the nice pale yellow shade, and appreciate its warmth, with one noting it's perfect for cold fall days. The size receives mixed feedback, with some finding it true to size while others describe it as very oversized. The quality and weight also get mixed reviews, with some sayi

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this sweater
items.body: I really like this sweater I’m usually either a medium to a larger in shirts so I never know what to buy. I bought the medium and it was perfect. Loose and stylish. The material is soft, not itchy, and it washes well. I washed it on cold and delicate and let it air dry. I got so many compliments on it at work. Even my students complimented my outfit. I wore it with black wide leg trouser style yoga pants in black and a pair boots with thin heels. I’m about 5’3 and 150-160 pounds and it was very complimentary. Read more
items.author: Gatsbygirl

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Oversized beauty
items.body: Oversized beauty. I normally size up in sweaters but I decided not to since it states that it’s oversized. A L would’ve been too big for me. M is perfect, keeps me warm and enough room for layers. I plan on getting it in more colors. Finally something of quality off Amazon. Read more
items.author: Andreea

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Warm, cute, pills
items.body: I like it. It's cute without looking too young on me. It's warm, enough that I brought a backup for teaching (but was ok in sweater). It pills like crazy and you definitely need to line dry. But I line dry a lot of my clothes anyway. So... for the price I'm very happy. Read more
items.author: Mary Ellen Wessels

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfy must have
items.body: Great sweater. Love the oversized look. Love the color. Warm but not thick! Super comfy. Can dress down or up. Purchased a large. Bought in black and khaki. But trust and purchase Read more
items.author: carrie

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Save your money!
items.body: I really wanted this sweater to work . I wish I could find at least a couple of brands on Amazon that were of some quality.This was way oversized. The material was flimsy and just poorly made, unfinished look. Sizing down would not have helped. For the price, shop quality brands on sale and get better quality often for less. I absolutely love Amazon and for the convenience I really want their fashion to work. Read more
items.author: Betty Mills

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Sleeves are gigantic
items.body: Nice material but HUGE sleeves. I wanted over sized but the sleeves were wild. Super comfy but I was swimming in its arms! Read more
items.author: Tosha

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars So Soft and Stylish
items.body: So soft and covers without clinging to a not so perfect body. The thickness is perfect, like a midweight. I love it! I even had to reorder a smaller size because it really is oversized. I bought two, one blue and one black. Read more
items.author: rita bowen

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful sweater
items.body: Such a comfortable sweater Im usually a medium and I bought a medium. Could have gone with a small but I like the oversized fit. I’ll probably put in Dryer when I wash it. Seems very well made. FP vibes! Read more
items.author: Kathy M

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Brown, Deep Green, Blue, Dark Khaki, Burgundy, Dark Grey, Apricot, Black, Camel, Brick Red, Light Blue, Red, Khaki, Pink. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
